{"tid":213801,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 古洞青山公路上執到隻狗 唔知點做!!!","createTime":"2017-04-23T11:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T02:26:00.000Z","uid":58858,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a0b53b09e6b70088ca60c8f8defe84f33ba9f0f","tid":213801,"uid":58858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:09:28.000Z","msg":"有朋友尋晚係青山公路上執到隻狗狗，真係公路中間發現，嚇撚死<br />\n帶左佢去寵物店查晶片，只查到晶片號碼，<br />\n帶左佢沖涼， 暫時寄託在朋友家中，<br />\n如果有人走失依隻狗狗請聯絡61219291 歐陽先生。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">想問如果有晶片號碼係咪可以去漁護處查狗主，<br />\n但好驚俾佢地知道係失狗又無人認領之後會送去SPCA....</span> </strong><br />\n另外想問可以放上邊度FB GROUP問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QhPP184.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQhPP184.jpg&h=ecd0c663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係依個位執到狗狗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4BNT7AP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4BNT7AP.jpg&h=3dc0ec1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有著衫的，似係有人養<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mh7StSF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMh7StSF.jpg&h=2d6fcdd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n帶左返去沖涼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NqfHF80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNqfHF80.jpg&h=909ac4ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 主人快啲黎接返我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb47e08417a58f8ce14fcf16e408e7ce602c5012","tid":213801,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9482bf76e17e1b6ea76f4837be5156324796ec1","tid":213801,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017